NUMBER 867
NAME Black abyss
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
The white sameness of the great ice sheet is broken here by a jagged black ravine that cuts across its surface like a deep wound. There is a large updraft of air from below yet you don't see anyway down to its source. Some distance to the northwest, a large mountain range looms on the horizon.
*DESCRIPTION_END
OUTDOOR_FLOOR
DAY_LIGHT
CHANNEL 853
REGION 51
CALL 16
;MONSTER_GROUP 84
ITEM 8 1567
EXIT W 866
